OL,3,CBeach closed to swimmers due to
OL,4,Cpollution for fifth time in three weeks
OL,6,FTwo beaches in Devon have been closed
OL,7,Fto swimmers due to pollution -
OL,8,Fincluding one for the fifth time in
OL,9,Fthree weeks.
OL,11,FEast Devon District Council issued
OL,12,Fwarnings for the beaches in Budleigh
OL,13,FSalterton and Exmouth after the
OL,14,FEnvironment Agency issued pollution
OL,15,Frisk warnings on 5 September.
OL,17,FIt means beachgoers are being advised
OL,18,Fto stay out of the water and red flags
OL,19,Fare being flown on both beaches.
