OL,3,CBeach closed to swimmers due to
OL,4,Cpollution for fifth time in three weeks
OL,6,FSouth West Water said there was a
OL,7,Fsmall spill from the temporary tank
OL,8,Ffeeding the overland pipeline at the
OL,9,Fsite the company was working on in
OL,10,FExmouth on 30 August.
OL,12,FThis led to SWW apologising and the
OL,13,Fbeach closing the following day.
OL,15,FSWW insisted it was carrying out
OL,16,Frepairs to the burst pipe "24 hours a
OL,17,Fday to make sure the repair is fixed
OL,18,Fquickly and is resilient for the
OL,19,Ffuture".
