OL,3,CBeach closed to swimmers due to
OL,4,Cpollution for fifth time in three weeks
OL,6,FThe company blames "sudden and heavy
OL,7,Frainfall in Exmouth overnight" causing
OL,8,Ftheir storm overflow to lead to a
OL,9,Fpollution incident.
OL,11,F"We are doing everything we can to
OL,12,Fprotect the environment as we work
OL,13,Faround the clock", SWW added.
OL,15,FEast Devon District Council announces
OL,16,Fthe beach is closed, the day after it
OL,17,Fwas reopened due to the previous spill.
OL,19,FITV West Country has contacted SWW for
OL,20,Fcomment.
